'''lathe'''

=== Pronunciation ===
*[[w:IPA|IPA]] /leɪð/
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]] /leID/

=== Noun ===
# a [[machine]] [[tool]] used to shape a piece of material, or [[workpiece]], by rotating the workpiece against a cutting tool.  See [[w:lathe]] for image and details.
#: ''He shaped the bedpost by turning it on a lathe.''

